BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Guys presented by THP Second Stage
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260911T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260911T213000
DTSTAMP:20260721T153610Z
UID:occ-2703@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Anne Nelson's two-hander: a fire captain and the editor who he
 lps him write eulogies after 9/11.\n\nAnne Nelson's drama drawn from a tru
 e story: in the weeks after September 11\, 2001\, a New York fire captain 
 has to eulogize the firefighters he lost and can't find the words\, so an 
 editor sits down to help him turn memories into tributes. Just two actors\
 , and more warmth and humor in it than the premise suggests. From the Henr
 y Players' Second Stage series\; runs 75 minutes with one intermission.
GEO:33.4486439;-84.1418279
LAST-MODIFIED:20260721T153558Z
LOCATION:The Henry Players Theater\, 136 Hood St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.simpletix.com/e/the-guys-presented-by-thp-second-stage-tic
 kets-283661
END:VEVENT
